✅ A) Setup
git --version → Check Git version
git config --global user.name → Set username
git config --global user.email → Set email
✅ B) Create Repo
git init → Create new repo
git clone URL → Copy repo
✅ C) Status
git status → Check file state
✅ D) Add Files
git add file → Stage file
git add . → Stage all files
✅ E) Commit
git commit -m "msg" → Save changes
git commit --amend → Edit last commit
✅ F) History
git log → Full history
git log --oneline → Short history
✅ G) Branch
git branch → List branches
git branch name → Create branch
git checkout name → Switch branch
git checkout -b name → Create + switch
✅ H) Merge
git merge branch → Merge branch
✅ I) Remote
git remote add origin URL → Connect repo
git push → Upload code
git pull → Download + merge
git fetch → Download only
✅ J) Undo
git restore file → Discard changes
git reset --hard → Delete changes
git revert id → Undo commit safely
✅ K) Stash
git stash → Save temp work
git stash pop → Restore work
✅ L) Tag
git tag v1.0 → Create version
git push origin v1.0 → Push tag
  
